老鹰乐队在首场 Sphere 演出中将《Heartache Tonight》献给已故合作者 JD Souther https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-dedicate-heartache-tonight-to-late-collaborator-jd-souther-at-first-sphere-show-3795923?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=eagles-今晚将心痛献给迟到的合作者 jd-souther-at-first-sphere-showLaura Molloy Sun, 22 Sep 2024 09:58:07 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3795923 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="老鹰队的唐·亨利。图片来源：西蒙·乔伊纳/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>唐·亨利告诉观众，这位词曲作者“在老鹰队中发挥了关键作用”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-dedicate-heartache-tonight-to-late-collaborator-jd-souther-at-first-sphere-show-3795923">老鹰乐队在第一场 Sphere 演出中向已故合作者 JD Souther 献上的歌曲《Heartache Tonight》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="老鹰队的唐·亨利。图片来源：西蒙·乔伊纳/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Don-Henley-of-The-Eagles.-CREDIT_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eagles">老鹰乐队</a>在 Las Vegas Sphere 驻场演出的第一晚，以歌曲《Heartache Tonight》向已故合作者 JD Souther 致敬。</p><p>美国创作型歌手兼演员 JD Souther <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jd-souther-singer-and-eagles-co-writer-has-died-aged-78-3794699">于本周早些时候去世，享年 78 岁</a>。老鹰队的一名代表首先证实了他的死讯，他告诉《 <a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2024-09-17/jd-souther-songwriter-eagles-linda-ronstadt-dead" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>洛杉矶时报》</em></a> ，他在新墨西哥州的家中“平静”地去世。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-pay-tribute-to-extraordinary-late-collaborator-jd-souther-3795051">周四（9 月 19 日），乐队通过他们的网站向 Souther 致敬</a>，写道：“我们失去了一位兄弟、一位朋友和一位出色的合作者，世界失去了一位伟大的歌曲作者，一位南加州声音的先驱，出现于 20 世纪 70 年代。”</p><p>现在，他们将情感丰富的《Heartache Tonight》献给了 Souther，他是这首 1979 年歌曲的共同创作者。周五（9 月 20 日），他们在内华达州大型广场举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-announce-las-vegas-sphere-residency-3765557">驻场</a>首场演出中演奏了这首歌。</p><p> “如果我没有向几个人致谢，那就是我的失职，”唐·亨利在播放这首歌之前告诉观众，这是当晚的最后一首歌曲。 “我要感谢三天前我们失去的那首歌的联合作者，JD Souther 先生。你可能知道 JD 在老鹰队中发挥了关键作用。他不是乐队成员，但他确实与我们共同创作了一些最热门的歌曲。”</p><p>亨利还向<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jimmy-buffett-has-died-aged-76-3492583">去年去世、享年 76 岁的歌曲作家吉米·巴菲特</a>致敬。 “唱出来，这样他们就能听到你的声音，”他说。</p><p>观看以下粉丝录制的视频： </p><p><iframe title="Heartache Tonight - 老鹰队，开幕之夜，拉斯维加斯，2024 年 9 月 20 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fB5Kuza5D2k?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>周五，在他们登上拉斯维加斯的舞台之前不久，吉他手乔·沃尔什向索瑟表达了自己的敬意。 “我的朋友，我的兄弟，也是我最喜欢的破坏房间的伙伴，JD 与人共同创作了描绘老鹰队飞行路线的歌曲。祝你好运。是时候回家了，”他在 Instagram 上写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAJiMwTu120/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.14