查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 透露“严重抑郁症”诊断https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-reveals-severe-depression-diagnosis-3795902?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=chappell-roan-reveals-severe-depression-diagnosisLaura Molloy Sun, 22 Sep 2024 08:12:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsLet’s Talk – mental healthPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3795902 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我想这是因为我的整个生活都改变了。现在我真正喜欢做的一切都带着包袱”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-reveals-severe-depression-diagnosis-3795902">查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 揭露“严重抑郁症”诊断的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-