nt/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3795517" class="wp-caption-text">查佩尔·罗恩（吉姆·戴森/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">前<em>《NME》</em>封面明星</a>还将成名比喻为“再次经历青春期”。 “我的身体确实感觉不一样了。它以一种非常不同的方式保持紧张：我有所有这些新的情绪，我真的很困惑。这就是12岁的感觉。</p><p> “我看着<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">[Lady] Gaga</a> ，甚至<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina [Carpenter]</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana [Del Rey]</a> ——当我看到他们在公共场合外出时，我什至无法想象他们为此做了多少准备。”</p><p>罗恩于 2022 年被诊断出患有 II 型双相情感障碍。今年早些时候，她在接受<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/chappell-roan-good-luck-babe-fame-fans-1235094314/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》杂志</em></a>采访时表示，她的名气迅速上升引发了一些症状。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CdooT-WhZLs/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F