sic-famous-interview-good-luck-babe"><em>《The Face》</em></a>采访时，这位歌手发泄了极端粉丝行为的常态化，包括“跟踪、在网上说废话、[那些人]不肯让你孤单、在公共场合对你大喊大叫”。她补充道：“我不知道感觉会这么糟糕。”</p><p>在她最初对粉丝行为发表评论以及随后的强烈反对后，一些女性艺术家为罗恩辩护，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/katy-perry">凯蒂·佩里</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muna">穆娜</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">麦莉·赛勒斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">博伊吉尼斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特。</a></p><p>这位“红酒超新星”歌手还表示，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">洛德</a>曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-lorde-sent-her-a-list-of-ways-to-cope-with-negativity-and-fame-3794353">与大家分享她年轻时应对名声和消极情绪的经历</a>。 “她给我发了一份我应该做的事情清单，”罗恩说。 “从字面上写下了八件事，她希望有人在她经历这件事时告诉她。她经历了该死的地狱。她还是个婴儿！” </p><figure id="attachment_3792894" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792894" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792894" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3792894" class="wp-caption-text">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 出席 2024 年 MTV VMA 颁奖典礼。图片来源：Mike Coppola/Getty Images for MTV</figcaption></figure><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mitski-welcomed-chappell-roan-to-the-shittiest-exclusive-club-in-the-world-and-warned-of-fandom-3792427">米茨基欢迎罗恩加入“世界上最糟糕的专属俱乐部”</a> ，警告她迅速崛起的负面影响，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Madison-Beer">麦迪逊·比尔</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-fame-is-like-an-abusive-ex-husband-3794622">最近也对罗恩关于处理名气和粉丝的评论进行了评论，她告诉<em>《NME</em> 》</a> ，她认为“很多人都认为 [Roan] 说的是错误的”。</p><p>在罗恩向粉丝们发布视频之前，她曾表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-shes-pumped-the-brakes-on-fame-after-fans-give-off-stalker-vibes-3775922">，在粉丝们散发出“跟踪者的氛围”后，她想“踩刹车”她的职业生涯</a>。她的言论赢得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Paramore">Paramore</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/aritsts/Hayley-Williams">Hayley Williams</a>的赞扬，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramores-hayley-williams-supports-chappell-roans-brave-and-unfortunately-necessary-boundary-comments-3787404">在 Instagram 上称赞这位流行歌星“勇敢”</a> 。</p><p>在本月早些时候的 MTV VMA 颁奖典礼上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-snaps-back-at-vmas-photographer-who-seemingly-told-her-to-shut-the-fuck-up-3792891">罗恩回击了一位摄影师，后者似乎告诉她在红地毯上“他妈的闭嘴”</a> 。</p><p>继 2023 年首张录音室专辑“The Rise And Fall Of A Midwest Princess”获得成功后，Roan 目前正在进行巡演。 <em>《NME》</em>在一篇<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/lollapalooza">四星评论</a>中将其描述为“罗恩大胆而厚颜无耻的笔的展示，她在其中将灼热的启示与一些可爱的厚颜无耻的合唱一起放置”。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>报道了她最近在伦敦 O2 Brixton 音乐学院的表演，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/chappell-roan-live-in-london-a-joyous-celebration-of-queerness-community-and-fun-3795515">一篇热情洋溢的五星级评论</a>中写道：“当她大摇大摆地走进来的那一刻，无可否认，查普尔·罗恩就是终极流行歌星”。</p><h2><strong>有关心理健康的帮助和建议：</strong></h2><ul><li> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/am-i-depressed-how-to-tell-2067753" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“我有抑郁症吗？” – 有关心理健康以及下一步该做什么的帮助和建议</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="https://musicindustrytherapists.com/">MITC – 音乐家行业治疗师的集体</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="https://www.tonicmusic.co.uk/tonic-rider" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TONIC Rider – 为音乐行业专业